AI CHAT SYSTEM
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ */

.chapter-ai-top{

    padding:
        22px 22px 18px;

    border-bottom:
        1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);

    display:flex;

    justify-content:space-between;

    align-items:center;

}

.chapter-ai-top h3{

    font-size:1.1rem;

    font-weight:850;

    letter-spacing:-.4px;

}

.chapter-ai-top p{

    margin-top:4px;

    font-size:.78rem;

    color:
        rgba(255,255,255,.60);

}

.chapter-ai-conversation{

    flex:1;

    overflow-y:auto;

    padding:20px;

    display:flex;

    flex-direction:column;

    gap:14px;

}

.ai-message{

    max-width:92%;

    padding:
        14px 16px;

    border-radius:18px;

    line-height:1.7;

    font-size:.84rem;

}

.ai-message-ai{

    background:
        rgba(255,255,255,.06);

    color:white;

    align-self:flex-start;

}

.ai-message-user{

    background:
        rgba(52,197,138,.16);

    color:white;

    align-self:flex-end;

}

.chapter-ai-suggestions{

    padding:
        0 18px 14px;

    display:flex;

    flex-wrap:wrap;

    gap:10px;

}

.suggestion-chip{

    min-height:34px;

    padding:
        0 14px;

    border-radius:999px;

    background:
        rgba(255,255,255,.06);

    color:white;

    cursor:pointer;

    font-size:.72rem;

    transition:
        all .34s var(--motion);

}

.suggestion-chip:hover{

    background:
        rgba(52,197,138,.16);

    color:
        #d8ffed;

}

.chapter-ai-input-area{

    padding:18px;

    border-top:
        1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);

    display:flex;

    gap:10px;

}

.chapter-ai-input-area textarea{

    flex:1;

    min-height:54px;

    max-height:140px;

    resize:none;

    border:none;

    outline:none;

    border-radius:18px;

    padding:14px 16px;

    font-family:inherit;

    background:
        rgba(255,255,255,.06);

    color:white;

}

.chapter-ai-input-area textarea::placeholder{

    color:
        rgba(255,255,255,.40);

}

#chapterAISend{

    min-width:84px;

    border-radius:18px;

    background:
        linear-gradient(
            135deg,
            rgba(52,197,138,.22),
            rgba(31,122,83,.18)
        );

    color:white;

    font-weight:760;

    cursor:pointer;

    transition:
        all .34s var(--motion);

}

#chapterAISend:hover{

    box-shadow:
        0 10px 20px rgba(52,197,138,.16);

}

/* AI CHAT SCROLLBAR */

.chapter-ai-conversation{

    scrollbar-width:thin;

    scrollbar-color:
        rgba(52,197,138,.24)
        transparent;

}

.chapter-ai-conversation::-webkit-scrollbar{

    width:8px;

}

.chapter-ai-conversation::-webkit-scrollbar-track{

    background:
        transparent;

}

.chapter-ai-conversation::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{

    background:
        rgba(52,197,138,.16);

    border-radius:999px;

    border:
        2px solid transparent;

    background-clip:padding-box;

}

.chapter-ai-conversation::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover{

    background:
        rgba(52,197,138,.30);

    background-clip:padding-box;

}

/* AI TYPING EFFECT */

.typing-message{

    padding:
        16px 18px;

}

.typing-wave{

    display:flex;

    align-items:center;

    gap:6px;

    min-height:20px;

}

.typing-wave span{

    width:8px;

    height:8px;

    border-radius:50%;

    background:
        rgba(52,197,138,.72);

    animation:
        aiWave 1s infinite ease-in-out;

}

.typing-wave span:nth-child(2){

    animation-delay:.15s;

}

.typing-wave span:nth-child(3){

    animation-delay:.30s;

}

@keyframes aiWave{

    0%,
    80%,
    100%{

        transform:scale(.7);

        opacity:.4;

    }

    40%{

        transform:scale(1);

        opacity:1;

    }

}

/* IOS AI TYPING EFFECT */

.typing-message{

    padding:
        14px 18px;

    background:
        rgba(255,255,255,.05);

    border:
        1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);

    backdrop-filter:
        blur(10px);

}

.typing-wave{

    display:flex;

    align-items:center;

    gap:7px;

    min-height:22px;

}

.typing-wave span{

    width:8px;

    height:8px;

    border-radius:50%;

    background:
        rgba(52,197,138,.78);

    animation:
        iosTyping 1.15s infinite ease-in-out;

    box-shadow:
        0 0 10px rgba(52,197,138,.18);

}

.typing-wave span:nth-child(2){

    animation-delay:.18s;

}

.typing-wave span:nth-child(3){

    animation-delay:.36s;

}

@keyframes iosTyping{

    0%{

        transform:
            translateY(0) scale(.82);

        opacity:.38;

    }

    25%{

        transform:
            translateY(-4px) scale(1);

        opacity:1;

    }

    50%{

        transform:
            translateY(0) scale(.9);

        opacity:.72;

    }

    100%{

        transform:
            translateY(0) scale(.82);

        opacity:.38;

    }

}

/* ULTRA SMOOTH ARTICLE SCROLL */

.modal-content{

    contain:layout style paint;

}

.accordion-content{

    transform:
        translateZ(0);

    backface-visibility:hidden;

}

.ordinance-text{

    transform:
        translateZ(0);

    backface-visibility:hidden;

    text-rendering:
        optimizeLegibility;

}